{"tid":979474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《大帥哥》完了，唔知有冇人記得張衛健嘅《神探方天謬》","createTime":"2019-01-12T17:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T08:22:35.000Z","uid":185765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"755f941c7db9ef31a53a3235559518a1bbe2757e","tid":979474,"uid":185765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T17:00:01.000Z","msg":"由於套電視劇太過偏門，應該冇乜巴絲識<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚟套戲02年播出，仲要喺濕鳩深圳台播<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果唔係唔覺意睇到張衛健嗰樣，真喺鬼先彩套戲。<br />\n唔睇唔知，一睇真喺好撚好睇啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一集無頭夜叉嗰頭同身嗰下分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，真喺嚇到當時仲年幼無知嘅小弟瀨屎瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，然後張衛健由傻仔變醒目仔嗰下真喺型到濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，太多不能盡述<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原版好彩喺粵語，如果大家得閒都真喺推薦睇下，宜家睇翻都喺咁撚好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，想多啲人知道套戲嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b36c20f0c22c578fd38c110f1adeab5058c617c","tid":979474,"uid":17488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"發燒變叻個個丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細細個睇唔識咩叫演技唔演技<br />\n淨係知個故事好吸引"},{"pid":"fca444522375935719be7f4cec5bf276662ab705","tid":979474,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T17:41:00.000Z","msg":"記得亞視好似有做過<br />\n結局好似好多打鬥場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ece050c3048d83f19f273aaabdf866fa1115435","tid":979474,"uid":125506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"依家想睇返<br />\n個陣好似佢變左做奸角殺曬D警察定咩"},{"pid":"fa1df30b4c2a88276d1e55325d437372d6520e2c","tid":979474,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"花非花"},{"pid":"ad78d5f8b9cd34286e5180952ab2379ee0aaa4bd","tid":979474,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"呢個二次創作正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TN73rnMbEDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTN73rnMbEDc&d=b%2BxmfEbLSqO0816Tk%2Fy04AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0f08b757\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TN73rnMbEDc</a><br />\n後尾真係搵到張衛健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/47dcV_DZwT0?t=604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F47dcV_DZ